'''Afghanistan Technical Vocational Institute (ATVI)''' ({{lang-ps|'''د افغانستان د تخنیکي مسلکي زده کړو انسټیټوټ'''}}) also known as ATVI,<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://atvi.edu.af/ |title=ATVI |access-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126143220/http://www.atvi.edu.af/ |archive-date=2017-01-26 |dead-url=yes |df= }}</ref><ref>[https://www.usaid.gov/news-information/fact-sheets/afghanistan-technical-vocational-institute-atvi usaid-news-information-atvi"]</ref> is a technical vocational institute in [[Afghanistan]]. ATVI is to provide market oriented technical and vocational training opportunities for Afghan youth
